m_q.target_metric: Score value for games against Portland with game numbers under 20
sub_questions: Which rows have 'Portland' in the Team column?
Which rows have Game values less than 20?
What is the intersection of these two conditions?
What is the Score value for the filtered row(s)?

format_notes: Game column contains numeric values as strings
Score column contains outcome prefix (W/L) followed by score with format 'L/W score1–score2 (OT)'
Some columns contain multiple values separated by commas (e.g., High rebounds with ties)
Location Attendance combines venue name and attendance count

constraints: Game number must be numeric and less than 20
Score format needs parsing to extract numeric values
derived_filters: Convert Game column from string to integer for numeric comparison
Extract score components from Score column (W/L indicator and point values)
output_format_requirements: Return the complete Score string value (e.g., 'L 97–98 (OT)')
If multiple matches exist, return all matching scores
If no matches exist, indicate no results found
